>schÃ©ma en barres</strong> est une reprÃ©sentation par\nrectangles qui permet de comparer, additionner ou rÃ©partir des quantitÃ©s\nvisuellement.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-example\">\n\n<p>Lors dâ€™une compÃ©tition de ski, 650 â‚¬ sont rÃ©partis entre les trois\npremiers. Le premier reÃ§oit deux fois plus que le troisiÃ¨me et le second\nreÃ§oit 50 â‚¬ de plus que le troisiÃ¨me.</p>\n<p>On reprÃ©sente la part du troisiÃ¨me par . On obtient le schÃ©ma\nci-dessous :</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/algebre-logique-cours/tikzpicture-2.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-2\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>Ainsi, le troisiÃ¨me reÃ§oit <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">150</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span></span></span></span>, le\nsecond <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">150</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">50</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">200</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span></span></span></span>\net le premier <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">Ã—</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">150</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">300</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Pour la fÃªte dâ€™un village, on organise une course cycliste. Une prime\ntotale de <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">320</span></span></span></span> â‚¬ sera rÃ©partie entre les trois\npremiers coureurs. Le premier touchera la prime dâ€™or, le deuxiÃ¨me la\nprime dâ€™argent et le troisiÃ¨me la prime de bronze.</p>\n<p>La prime dâ€™or sâ€™Ã©lÃ¨ve Ã  <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">70</span></span></span></span> â‚¬ de plus que la prime\ndâ€™argent, et la prime de bronze Ã  <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">80</span></span></span></span> â‚¬ de moins que\nla prime dâ€™argent.</p>\n<p>En utilisant un schÃ©ma en barres, donner la valeur en euros de\nchacune des primes.</p>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 2.5cm;\"></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<p>On reprÃ©sente le montant de la prime dâ€™argent par <img src=\"/images/sixieme/algebre-logique-cours/tikzpicture-3.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-3\">.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/algebre-logique-cours/tikzpicture-4.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-4\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>De ce schÃ©ma, on dÃ©duit :</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/algebre-logique-cours/tikzpicture-5.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-5\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>Ainsi, la prime dâ€™argent vaut <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">110</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span></span></span></span>, la\nprime dâ€™or vaut <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">110</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">70</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">180</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Â â‚¬</span></span></span></span></span> et la prime de bronze vaut <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0